sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Parent
    participant App as Flutter parent mode
    participant Outbox as Local offline outbox
    participant API as Next.js reminder API (BE-007)
    participant Caregiver as Caregiver device

    App-->>Parent: Full-screen medicine reminder
    alt Taken / Snooze / Skip while online
        Parent->>App: Select action
        App->>API: Idempotent reminder action
        API-->>App: Authoritative event state
        App-->>Parent: Action recorded
    else Action while offline
        Parent->>App: Select action
        App->>Outbox: Store action + idempotency key
        App-->>Parent: Saved offline, will sync
        Outbox->>API: Replay after reconnect
        API-->>Outbox: Accepted/already applied
    else Need Help
        Parent->>App: I need help
        App->>API: Escalate immediately
        API-->>Caregiver: Privacy-safe urgent notification
        App-->>Parent: Help request sent
    end
